description:
Rare video footage of Ted Greene giving a guitar lesson to Nick Stasinos Summer/September of 1999.

This lesson includes conversations on many topics, a few with musical examples. Most notably Ted does his best to define what American music is, inclusive of some uproarious comparisons.
My Life with The Chord Chemist: A Memoir of Ted Greene, Apotheosis of Solo Guitar by Barbara Franklin - Available at amazon.com
http://www.amazon.com/My-Life-Chord-Chemist-Apotheosis/dp/1449575579

Visit http://www.tedgreene.com for all things Ted
